>> Good morning and welcome to

00:00:26.806 --> 00:00:28.016
Auto Layout techniques in

00:00:28.016 --> 00:00:29.066
Interface Builder.

00:00:29.726 --> 00:00:30.826
I'm Jonathon Mah.

