00:16:44.436 --> 00:16:45.876
So let's go fix that.

00:16:50.296 --> 00:16:51.826
So, in Interface Builder,

00:16:52.356 --> 00:16:53.816
whoops, I'm going to jump back

00:16:53.816 --> 00:16:53.986
